*Multiple Equilibrium Equations*

1. *Model-independent binding equation*: Adair’s equation Macroscopic or statistical binding constant; not refer to specific binding sites


  1. Adair’s equation makes no assumptions about the two sites.
  2. Even if the two sites are identical, K 1 and K 2 will be different.
  3. STATISTICAL binding constants: do not refer to "site 1" and "site 2"


